in Dongguan killed three people.

83
00:04:41,780 --> 00:04:48,840
Plus, “As of mid-March, there have been
15 motorcycle accidents and 17 deaths in the

84
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:50,470
city this year.

85
00:04:50,470 --> 00:04:58,470
From 2018 to 2020, 814 people were killed
in traffic accidents involving motorcycles

86
00:04:58,470 --> 00:05:05,820
