111
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:42,350
Perfect.

112
00:06:42,350 --> 00:06:46,110
So what happens to all the confiscated scooters
and motorcycles?

113
00:06:46,110 --> 00:06:51,310
Some videos show motorcycles getting crushed
and recycled in junkyards.

114
00:06:51,310 --> 00:06:53,650
But it seems there’s more to it.

115
00:06:53,650 --> 00:06:58,330
This photo shows a ticket for 1,200 RMB—about
$180.

116
00:06:58,330 --> 00:07:03,490
It was given to a citizen who requested their
motorcycle be returned.

117
00:07:03,490 --> 00:07:08,120
So some people believe this whole confiscation
policy is just a way for local authorities

118
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:09,740
to make money.

119
00:07:09,740 --> 00:07:12,870
They take your bike, and you have to pay them
to get it back.

120
